  "description": "The tidal pulse as a migration engine — tidalDepth at 0.7 creates a slow filter sweep that covers a full octave of frequency space every 5 seconds. FM adds harmonic sideband content that the tidal sweep reveals and conceals in sequence. The sound migrates through the filter continuously.",
