    "revelation": "The tidal filter sweep and the FM sideband content interact: as the tide moves the filter cutoff, different sidebands are highlighted and suppressed in turn. The sound changes character every 2 seconds without any MIDI input.",
    "diagnosis": "Tidal Migration is the BREATHE macro fully realized. tidalDepth=0.7 + tidalRate=0.2 Hz creates a smooth 5-second sweep. FM at OscA provides the sideband content for the sweep to reveal. This preset requires no performance — it performs itself."
